name: Crowned Heads - Four Kicks Black Belt Buckle - Corona Gorda
brand: Crowned Heads, Four Kicks Black Belt Buckle
additionalNotes: Already a highly-rated star in the Crowned Heads stable, Four Kicks has undergone a transformation of the highest order: now clad in a dark, enticing Connecticut broadleaf maduro wrapper, Four Kicks Black Belt Buckle's all-Nicaraguan core is amplified with naturally sweet tobacco flavors in a way that can only be described as "scrumptious".
